1
00:00:38,140 --> 00:00:40,660
♪The blade dance
causing ripples to spread across the lake♪

2
00:00:40,660 --> 00:00:43,620
♪Waving the banner amidst the storm and rain♪

3
00:00:44,260 --> 00:00:46,900
♪The snow is not bothered
by the sadness and the happiness♪

4
00:00:46,900 --> 00:00:49,620
♪Blazing through the desert
with the rein in hands♪

5
00:00:49,620 --> 00:00:52,820
♪Young and inexperienced, it is apparent♪

6
00:00:53,140 --> 00:00:55,700
♪Bold ambition
interspersed with recklessness♪

7
00:00:55,700 --> 00:00:58,900
♪Mind not the predestination♪

8
00:00:58,900 --> 00:01:01,940
♪Solving all the problems
that fate presents me♪

9
00:01:01,940 --> 00:01:03,420
♪From all the trials and hardship♪

10
00:01:03,420 --> 00:01:05,180
♪Spawn the vast courage♪

11
00:01:05,180 --> 00:01:06,900
♪The journey to seek glory and justice♪

12
00:01:06,900 --> 00:01:08,500
♪Is not in vain♪

13
00:01:08,500 --> 00:01:10,220
♪One smile is all it takes
to get what you're thinking♪

14
00:01:10,220 --> 00:01:13,540
♪A ballad to our journey♪

15
00:01:14,900 --> 00:01:18,020
♪Pursuing the dream of our youth♪

16
00:01:18,020 --> 00:01:20,980
♪We take everything as it comes♪

17
00:01:21,180 --> 00:01:24,180
♪The distant land might be dangerous♪

18
00:01:24,180 --> 00:01:27,020
♪But what's life without an adventure?♪

19
00:01:27,020 --> 00:01:30,100
♪Youths are supposed to dream big and be sharp♪

20
00:01:30,340 --> 00:01:33,420
♪Every struggle in life has taught us♪

21
00:01:33,420 --> 00:01:35,380
♪That we shall do what we can wherever we go♪

22
00:01:35,380 --> 00:01:40,900
♪Together, another journey awaits♪

23
00:01:44,560 --> 00:01:50,020
[The Blood of Youth]

24
00:01:50,020 --> 00:01:52,740
[Episode 3]

25
00:02:09,900 --> 00:02:11,220
(You didn't let me down.)

26
00:02:12,260 --> 00:02:13,260
(But that)

27
00:02:14,340 --> 00:02:15,820
(won't delay him for too long.)

28
00:02:32,140 --> 00:02:34,020
After witnessing the Fatal Blossom Shower,

29
00:02:34,980 --> 00:02:36,900
pretending to be asleep was worth it.

30
00:02:39,060 --> 00:02:39,740
Wuxin.

31
00:02:43,980 --> 00:02:46,060
Wuchan, it's been a long time.

32
00:03:06,660 --> 00:03:07,900
There's somewhere I want to go.

33
00:03:08,500 --> 00:03:09,580
I wonder if this young friend

34
00:03:10,100 --> 00:03:11,900
would like to go with me.

35
00:03:15,060 --> 00:03:15,700
No.

36
00:03:17,980 --> 00:03:19,420
Hypocrite.

37
00:03:21,500 --> 00:03:22,060
What do you want?

38
00:03:30,940 --> 00:03:31,460
What does that mean?

39
00:03:32,410 --> 00:03:33,500
It looks like this young friend

40
00:03:34,660 --> 00:03:36,100
is also willing to travel together.

41
00:03:37,380 --> 00:03:38,500
That's great.

42
00:03:45,100 --> 00:03:45,500
Wuxin!

43
00:03:49,540 --> 00:03:50,500
Wangyou,

44
00:03:51,140 --> 00:03:52,180
in the end,

45
00:03:52,380 --> 00:03:53,860
you eventually chose this path.

46
00:03:54,580 --> 00:03:56,940
Twelve years ago, I told you

47
00:03:57,660 --> 00:03:59,500
that sooner or later, you would face disaster

48
00:03:59,660 --> 00:04:00,980
because of that lad, Wuxin.

49
00:04:01,940 --> 00:04:03,540
Have you ever regretted

50
00:04:03,620 --> 00:04:04,620
the decision you made back then?

51
00:04:06,900 --> 00:04:08,980
Of course you won't regret it.

52
00:04:09,820 --> 00:04:10,900
You said

53
00:04:11,660 --> 00:04:13,500
you wished to come back here and have a look

54
00:04:13,700 --> 00:04:15,180
before you die.

55
00:04:17,020 --> 00:04:19,700
I'll hold a memorial service for you here today.

56
00:04:20,100 --> 00:04:22,980
I hope your soul will return to your home.

57
00:04:34,460 --> 00:04:36,060
[Lord Yong'an, Xiao Chuhe, namely Xiao Se, showed up.]

58
00:04:36,060 --> 00:04:37,660
[He was taken away
from Belle's Manor by Ye Anshi.]

59
00:04:37,660 --> 00:04:38,300
Xiao Se?

60
00:04:40,420 --> 00:04:41,580
My dear disciple,

61
00:04:44,140 --> 00:04:45,700
[Ji Ruofeng, Head of Baixiao Sect]
it's time for us to meet.

62
00:05:04,140 --> 00:05:04,660
Xiao Se,

63
00:05:05,380 --> 00:05:07,660
why don't we grab this chance and run?

64
00:05:08,300 --> 00:05:09,940
Sure, I wish you the best of luck.

65
00:05:13,260 --> 00:05:14,940
Why aren't you coming?

66
00:05:15,860 --> 00:05:17,260
I'm sure you've seen his qinggong.

67
00:05:18,060 --> 00:05:19,460
Do you think we can outrun him?

68
00:05:20,740 --> 00:05:21,100
Then...

69
00:05:21,940 --> 00:05:22,740
Then we'll run

70
00:05:22,980 --> 00:05:23,740
after we knock him unconscious.

71
00:05:24,300 --> 00:05:25,940
Sure, I wish you success.

72
00:05:27,340 --> 00:05:28,940
We can't beat him or outrun him.

73
00:05:29,140 --> 00:05:30,060
How can great men like us

74
00:05:30,460 --> 00:05:31,700
be held hostage here?

75
00:05:33,940 --> 00:05:35,020
I never said we can't escape.

76
00:05:35,740 --> 00:05:36,980
But we need to find a place we can survive

77
00:05:36,980 --> 00:05:37,980
after we escape from him.

78
00:05:38,740 --> 00:05:39,780
This place is deserted

79
00:05:40,620 --> 00:05:41,420
with nothing here.

80
00:05:41,900 --> 00:05:43,100
You're also heavily injured.

81
00:05:43,700 --> 00:05:44,500
If we got lost,

82
00:05:44,940 --> 00:05:45,980
we could die.

83
00:05:50,100 --> 00:05:51,020
Look at you.

84
00:05:51,700 --> 00:05:52,340
No one would expect

85
00:05:52,420 --> 00:05:53,660
you're Lei Hong's disciple.

86
00:05:55,980 --> 00:05:57,020
Do you know my master?

87
00:05:57,300 --> 00:05:57,860
Of course.

88
00:05:59,060 --> 00:06:00,660
He was one of the Four Heroes of the Lei Clan
back then.

89
00:06:01,820 --> 00:06:03,020
He may be an external disciple.

90
00:06:03,580 --> 00:06:05,540
But at a young age, he managed to restore

91
00:06:05,980 --> 00:06:07,180
the lost skills of Fire Infusion

92
00:06:07,180 --> 00:06:08,060
with an incomplete book.

93
00:06:09,380 --> 00:06:10,300
When he was at his peak,

94
00:06:11,260 --> 00:06:12,780
his reputation was superior
to the current clan leader,

95
00:06:12,860 --> 00:06:13,900
Lei Qianhu.

96
00:06:16,100 --> 00:06:17,420
My master rarely

97
00:06:17,500 --> 00:06:18,460
talks about himself.

98
00:06:19,140 --> 00:06:20,580
He prefers staying alone.

99
00:06:21,180 --> 00:06:23,420
He'd either stare at the sky or the flowers.

100
00:06:24,580 --> 00:06:25,380
So how much do you know

101
00:06:25,420 --> 00:06:26,380
about my master?

102
00:06:26,700 --> 00:06:27,420
Can you tell me?

103
00:06:31,500 --> 00:06:32,140
It's said

104
00:06:32,780 --> 00:06:33,580
the ancestor of the Lei Clan

105
00:06:33,620 --> 00:06:35,460
once held the ceremony
of hanging up their swords and blades.

106
00:06:36,540 --> 00:06:37,860
They were determined to abandon the use

107
00:06:37,900 --> 00:06:39,340
of the two most commonly used weapons
in the martial arts world.

108
00:06:41,180 --> 00:06:42,780
They embarked on a completely different path

109
00:06:43,780 --> 00:06:45,420
by focusing on developing explosive weapons,

110
00:06:46,060 --> 00:06:47,020
which shocked the martial arts world.

111
00:06:49,100 --> 00:06:50,500
But your master went against
the ancestral teaching

112
00:06:51,260 --> 00:06:51,980
and practiced swordsmanship.

113
00:06:53,020 --> 00:06:54,460
He combined it
with the Lei Clan's explosive techniques

114
00:06:54,540 --> 00:06:56,060
and invented the Shabu.

115
00:06:57,820 --> 00:07:00,300
When the sword came into existence,
the thunder roared

116
00:07:00,940 --> 00:07:02,060
and the flame was blazing.

117
00:07:02,940 --> 00:07:04,700
He made a name for himself
as he journeyed the martial arts world

118
00:07:05,260 --> 00:07:06,220
with the sword.

119
00:07:07,500 --> 00:07:08,420
In the end, he was defeated

120
00:07:08,420 --> 00:07:10,300
by Li Hanyi, the Xueyue Sword Deity,

121
00:07:10,820 --> 00:07:12,260
and is nowhere to be found ever since.

122
00:07:13,860 --> 00:07:14,580
Some said

123
00:07:14,820 --> 00:07:16,260
he returned to the Lei Fortress
to go into seclusion

124
00:07:16,460 --> 00:07:18,340
and claimed he wouldn't leave
until he becomes a sword deity.

125
00:07:19,220 --> 00:07:21,540
Some said the clan leader, Lei Qianhu,
expelled him from the Lei Clan

126
00:07:21,940 --> 00:07:23,860
because he went against the ancestral teaching.

127
00:07:25,980 --> 00:07:27,340
Those are just rumors.

128
00:07:27,940 --> 00:07:28,500
My master was never

129
00:07:28,540 --> 00:07:29,380
expelled from the Lei Clan.

130
00:07:30,500 --> 00:07:32,660
He... he was just...

131
00:07:35,740 --> 00:07:37,020
If you can't say it, don't say it.

132
00:07:38,060 --> 00:07:38,820
I'm not interested

133
00:07:38,940 --> 00:07:39,580
in the Lei Clan's secrets.

134
00:07:40,100 --> 00:07:40,820
I'm glad to hear

135
00:07:40,860 --> 00:07:41,660
he was not expelled from the Lei Clan.

136
00:07:44,220 --> 00:07:45,180
You sounded

137
00:07:45,820 --> 00:07:46,900
like you know my master.

138
00:07:48,620 --> 00:07:49,100
I don't know him.

139
00:07:50,700 --> 00:07:52,100
Why do you look relieved

140
00:07:52,420 --> 00:07:53,900
when you heard that he was not
expelled from the Lei Clan?

141
00:07:55,820 --> 00:07:57,260
If he were expelled from the Lei Clan,

142
00:07:57,540 --> 00:07:58,380
it doesn't matter if it's Xueyue City

143
00:07:58,780 --> 00:07:59,780
or the Lei Fortress,

144
00:08:01,380 --> 00:08:02,340
who would help his foolish disciple,

145
00:08:02,380 --> 00:08:03,860
who lost the Shabu,

146
00:08:03,900 --> 00:08:04,580
pay his debt?

147
00:08:05,820 --> 00:08:06,780
After everything you said,

148
00:08:07,060 --> 00:08:07,700
it's all

149
00:08:07,740 --> 00:08:08,900
because of that 500 silver taels.

150
00:08:11,660 --> 00:08:12,060
Wait.

151
00:08:12,740 --> 00:08:13,500
What did you just say?

152
00:08:14,060 --> 00:08:14,460
Pay up.

153
00:08:15,140 --> 00:08:15,860
No, before that.

154
00:08:16,500 --> 00:08:18,100
The foolish disciple who lost the Shabu.

155
00:08:19,620 --> 00:08:20,100
Shabu.

156
00:08:21,980 --> 00:08:22,460
Oh, no.

157
00:08:22,900 --> 00:08:23,260
I'm so dead.

158
00:08:23,780 --> 00:08:24,500
How could I lose

159
00:08:24,540 --> 00:08:25,380
the Shabu?

160
00:08:31,740 --> 00:08:32,700
Misfortune has befallen the Lei Clan.

161
00:08:36,900 --> 00:08:37,740
How's your injury?

162
00:08:39,620 --> 00:08:40,340
It's nothing serious.

163
00:08:41,060 --> 00:08:42,620
It just hurts when I try to use my skills.

164
00:08:44,420 --> 00:08:45,340
White-Haired Deity's martial arts skills

165
00:08:45,500 --> 00:08:46,340
are unfathomable.

166
00:08:47,020 --> 00:08:48,060
We were lucky

167
00:08:48,660 --> 00:08:49,660
to be able to survive.

168
00:08:50,620 --> 00:08:51,100
You're right about that.

169
00:08:52,140 --> 00:08:52,940
Speaking of which,

170
00:08:53,900 --> 00:08:55,140
it's all thanks to his help.

171
00:09:07,900 --> 00:09:10,180
They killed my father!

172
00:09:10,540 --> 00:09:13,180
I want to kill all of them!

173
00:09:22,580 --> 00:09:23,820
Amitabha.

174
00:09:25,780 --> 00:09:28,020
If this vicious cycle continues,
when will it all end?

175
00:09:28,340 --> 00:09:30,820
[Dajue, Jiulong Sect]
Besides, he's still a child.

176
00:09:37,780 --> 00:09:39,180
Amitabha.

177
00:10:20,180 --> 00:10:20,780
How many things

178
00:10:21,180 --> 00:10:22,500
have happened to you along the way?

179
00:10:23,220 --> 00:10:24,340
You have so many injuries.

180
00:10:27,060 --> 00:10:27,540
It's all right.

181
00:10:28,220 --> 00:10:28,860
I'm used to it.

182
00:10:43,900 --> 00:10:44,740
Where's Master Wuchan?

183
00:10:45,300 --> 00:10:45,980
I need to ask him

184
00:10:46,940 --> 00:10:48,140
about Wuxin.

185
00:11:01,540 --> 00:11:01,940
Wait here.

186
00:11:24,860 --> 00:11:25,900
I've read a book

187
00:11:26,780 --> 00:11:28,260
that said there are deities in the world.

188
00:11:29,420 --> 00:11:31,460
They could stand on clouds and dress in white.

189
00:11:32,090 --> 00:11:33,180
They can live without food,

190
00:11:33,980 --> 00:11:35,420
travel far with the wind,

191
00:11:36,060 --> 00:11:37,140
and never grow old.

192
00:11:38,220 --> 00:11:39,780
It's describing someone like him, right?

193
00:11:41,380 --> 00:11:42,140
I've never met anyone

194
00:11:42,180 --> 00:11:43,220
who masters such incredible qinggong.

195
00:11:44,340 --> 00:11:46,580
It really felt like riding the wind.

196
00:11:47,700 --> 00:11:48,780
It took us so long to get here.

197
00:11:49,220 --> 00:11:50,620
But he doesn't look exhausted at all.

198
00:11:51,500 --> 00:11:52,580
It's incredible.

199
00:11:53,020 --> 00:11:53,820
As his hostages,

200
00:11:53,860 --> 00:11:55,060
here we are complimenting him.

201
00:11:56,020 --> 00:11:57,020
What do you think he would feel

202
00:11:57,060 --> 00:11:57,980
if he heard us?

203
00:11:58,300 --> 00:11:59,060
Both of you

204
00:12:00,100 --> 00:12:01,260
aren't my hostages.

205
00:12:02,900 --> 00:12:03,900
As I said earlier,

206
00:12:04,660 --> 00:12:05,380
I want you

207
00:12:06,260 --> 00:12:07,180
to accompany me to a place.

208
00:12:08,220 --> 00:12:09,300
There were so many of us in the carriage.

209
00:12:09,540 --> 00:12:10,540
Why did you

210
00:12:10,540 --> 00:12:11,220
have to pick us?

211
00:12:11,980 --> 00:12:12,700
You picked us

212
00:12:12,780 --> 00:12:13,660
because one of us doesn't know martial arts

213
00:12:14,620 --> 00:12:15,980
and the other one is seriously injured.

214
00:12:18,180 --> 00:12:19,300
Seriously injured?

215
00:12:22,580 --> 00:12:23,300
I may not be skillful.

216
00:12:24,220 --> 00:12:25,420
But I'm willing to help.

217
00:12:26,700 --> 00:12:28,300
You want to treat my injuries?

218
00:12:30,700 --> 00:12:31,300
During this journey,

219
00:12:31,860 --> 00:12:33,380
I still need your help.

220
00:12:34,380 --> 00:12:35,340
So of course, I'll help you

221
00:12:36,420 --> 00:12:37,300
treat your injuries.

222
00:12:40,300 --> 00:12:42,060
I think I'll pass.

223
00:12:44,980 --> 00:12:46,100
You were injured by the White-Haired Deity's

224
00:12:46,220 --> 00:12:47,060
zhenqi.
(*true energy)

225
00:12:47,500 --> 00:12:48,340
If you use your skills,

226
00:12:49,260 --> 00:12:50,820
two different energies will clash.

227
00:12:51,700 --> 00:12:53,220
It certainly will make your injuries even worse.

228
00:12:54,140 --> 00:12:55,820
I'll help you

229
00:12:55,900 --> 00:12:57,420
force out his zhenqi from your body.

230
00:12:59,260 --> 00:12:59,860
(There truly)

231
00:13:00,540 --> 00:13:02,420
(is such mystical qinggong in the world.)

232
00:13:07,220 --> 00:13:07,980
I can't swim.

233
00:13:44,140 --> 00:13:44,980
What kind of skill

234
00:13:48,340 --> 00:13:49,980
could make him stand on water?

235
00:13:50,980 --> 00:13:52,140
It wasn't me.

236
00:13:52,900 --> 00:13:53,740
He did it himself.

237
00:13:55,420 --> 00:13:56,540
(Lei Wujie did it himself?)

238
00:13:57,060 --> 00:13:57,900
Old Wangyou told me

239
00:13:58,100 --> 00:13:59,300
people with conscience and flexibility

240
00:13:59,940 --> 00:14:01,220
can become one with nature.

241
00:14:02,340 --> 00:14:03,740
Turns out he didn't lie to me.

242
00:14:22,220 --> 00:14:22,580
Break!

243
00:14:50,300 --> 00:14:50,740
It was a success.

244
00:14:51,500 --> 00:14:52,020
You can take him back.

245
00:14:54,620 --> 00:14:55,260
How do you feel?

246
00:14:56,700 --> 00:14:57,100
I feel a tingling

247
00:14:58,180 --> 00:14:58,900
and numbing sensation all over.

248
00:14:59,820 --> 00:15:00,820
I feel better too.

249
00:15:02,820 --> 00:15:03,620
The Lei Clan

250
00:15:03,700 --> 00:15:04,620
is a well-known family in the martial arts world.

251
00:15:05,140 --> 00:15:05,900
How did they produce

252
00:15:05,900 --> 00:15:06,980
such an airhead?

253
00:15:08,820 --> 00:15:10,780
That's not how you pronounce it.

254
00:15:11,420 --> 00:15:13,220
Use the falling tone.

255
00:15:14,900 --> 00:15:17,180
I'll pronounce it the way I want.

256
00:15:18,380 --> 00:15:18,940
Airhead.

257
00:15:19,780 --> 00:15:20,820
I'm serious. That's not how you pronounce it.

258
00:15:20,860 --> 00:15:22,580
I don't care.

259
00:15:22,940 --> 00:15:23,500
Airhead.

260
00:15:23,780 --> 00:15:24,340
Airhead.

261
00:15:25,140 --> 00:15:26,140
Why are you so stubborn?

262
00:15:26,660 --> 00:15:28,340
How nice.

263
00:15:32,740 --> 00:15:33,820
So Wuxin is the son of Ye Dingzhi,

264
00:15:33,900 --> 00:15:35,380
the Head of the Tianwaitian Sect.

265
00:15:36,100 --> 00:15:37,780
The one Tianwaitian sent to be held
as a hostage in Beili?

266
00:15:38,260 --> 00:15:38,660
Precisely.

267
00:15:40,220 --> 00:15:42,540
Twelve years ago, the Demon Sect started a war

268
00:15:42,780 --> 00:15:44,260
to overthrow the imperial power of Beili.

269
00:15:45,100 --> 00:15:46,060
That year, the Governor-General,

270
00:15:46,180 --> 00:15:46,860
Lord Langya,

271
00:15:46,940 --> 00:15:47,940
led the Three Armies of Beili,

272
00:15:48,540 --> 00:15:49,460
together with Tianqi's Four Guardians,

273
00:15:49,780 --> 00:15:51,060
joining forces with the power
of the whole martial arts world

274
00:15:51,500 --> 00:15:52,580
to defeat the Demon Sect.

275
00:15:53,460 --> 00:15:54,660
When Ye Dingzhi died,

276
00:15:55,140 --> 00:15:56,220
Wuxin was only five years old.

277
00:15:57,220 --> 00:15:58,660
Now, the 12-year armistice

278
00:15:58,700 --> 00:15:59,500
is almost up.

