501
00:25:05,540 --> 00:25:06,700
more than you do.

502
00:25:09,420 --> 00:25:09,780
But...

503
00:25:11,980 --> 00:25:12,900
Yes, money is saved.

504
00:25:30,660 --> 00:25:32,060
Long Arch Wing Chaser?

505
00:25:32,610 --> 00:25:33,820
Night Parade of 100 Ghosts?

