00:29:16,180 --> 00:29:16,900
at the camp of the Long Arch Wing Chaser

564
00:29:17,020 --> 00:29:18,300
and the Night Parade of 100 Ghosts.

565
00:29:19,300 --> 00:29:19,940
If we're not careful enough,

566
00:29:19,980 --> 00:29:21,140
we'll get caught,

567
00:29:21,700 --> 00:29:22,740
let alone rescue Lei Wujie.

568
00:29:24,540 --> 00:29:26,140
What's more, we don't know

569
00:29:26,180 --> 00:29:27,180
how many experts are here.

570
00:29:27,700 --> 00:29:28,540
With only you and me here,

571
00:29:28,940 --> 00:29:29,860
how are you planning to save him

572
00:29:30,220 --> 00:29:31,100
when I don't know martial arts at all?

573
00:29:33,580 --> 00:29:34,700
We'll plan as we go.

574
00:29:35,940 --> 00:29:36,940
We'll find a way eventually.

575
00:29:37,740 --> 00:29:38,900
But our priority

576
00:29:39,260 --> 00:29:40,300
is to capture someone.

577
00:29:41,220 --> 00:29:41,860
So we can ask him

578
00:29:42,300 --> 00:29:42,900
where Lei Wujie

579
00:29:42,940 --> 00:29:43,660
is being locked up.

580
00:29:44,860 --> 00:29:46,100
I had a good time.

581
00:29:46,700 --> 00:29:49,500
Let's go star-gazing after filling our tummies.

582
00:29:50,020 --> 00:29:50,580
All right.

583
00:29:52,540 --> 00:29:53,180
Here he comes.

584
00:29:54,260 --> 00:29:55,540
Forgive me for I'm going to sin.

585
00:29:59,060 --> 00:29:59,820
When you're ready

586
00:29:59,820 --> 00:30:00,500
to answer my question,

587
00:30:00,980 --> 00:30:01,660
tell me.

588
00:30:02,260 --> 00:30:03,020
I'll pull you up.

589
00:30:04,780 --> 00:30:06,180
I thought you know how to use the Abyssal Eye.

590
00:30:06,820 --> 00:30:07,420
Why aren't you using it?

591
00:30:08,420 --> 00:30:08,900
It's tiring.

592
00:30:12,660 --> 00:30:14,500
Did you really grow up in Hanshui Temple?

593
00:30:18,260 --> 00:30:19,100
Where else would I be

594
00:30:19,580 --> 00:30:20,420
if not Hanshui Temple?

595
00:30:23,380 --> 00:30:24,140
You have

596
00:30:24,700 --> 00:30:26,340
the Secret Rakshasa Arts.

597
00:30:27,900 --> 00:30:28,820
Those in the martial arts world

598
00:30:28,860 --> 00:30:29,900
will definitely keep a lookout for you.

599
00:30:31,460 --> 00:30:32,820
But not to the extent of involving

600
00:30:32,860 --> 00:30:34,620
the powerful Wushuang City to get into fights.

601
00:30:35,180 --> 00:30:36,700
Let alone the Tianwaitian Sect.

602
00:30:38,060 --> 00:30:39,900
After Tianwaitian lost the battle 12 years ago,

603
00:30:40,780 --> 00:30:41,900
they made a 12-year armistice

604
00:30:42,060 --> 00:30:43,460
with the major sects

605
00:30:44,020 --> 00:30:44,980
of the Central Plains.

606
00:30:45,940 --> 00:30:46,860
Within 12 years,

607
00:30:47,780 --> 00:30:48,860
no one from Tianwaitian

608
00:30:49,100 --> 00:30:50,220
is allowed to enter Beili.

609
00:30:51,620 --> 00:30:52,580
If I'm not mistaken,

610
00:30:53,420 --> 00:30:54,300
there was

611
00:30:54,380 --> 00:30:55,420
a five-year-old hostage at the time.

612
00:30:57,140 --> 00:30:57,900
The truth

613
00:30:58,460 --> 00:30:59,620
isn't as complicated as imagined.

614
00:31:00,780 --> 00:31:01,380
All of you think

615
00:31:01,380 --> 00:31:02,300
I'm someone important.

616
00:31:03,340 --> 00:31:03,900
But

617
00:31:06,060 --> 00:31:07,260
I'm nothing more than

618
00:31:08,700 --> 00:31:09,540
a mischievous disciple

619
00:31:09,620 --> 00:31:10,620
at Hanshui Temple.

620
00:31:12,340 --> 00:31:14,740
I'm sorry. I was out of line.

621
00:31:18,660 --> 00:31:19,140
Wuxin.

622
00:31:20,860 --> 00:31:21,260
Yes?

623
00:31:21,700 --> 00:31:23,060
If you don't pull him up,

624
00:31:23,740 --> 00:31:24,540
he'll die.

625
00:31:25,540 --> 00:31:25,940
Oh no!

626
00:31:29,780 --> 00:31:30,940
Judging from what you said,

627
00:31:31,420 --> 00:31:32,580
these two friends of yours

628
00:31:32,780 --> 00:31:33,940
are very interesting.

629
00:31:36,260 --> 00:31:37,060
If it weren't for them,

630
00:31:37,460 --> 00:31:38,300
would I be so unlucky

631
00:31:38,380 --> 00:31:39,260
and get caught here?

632
00:31:39,860 --> 00:31:40,700
If I see them again next time,

633
00:31:41,020 --> 00:31:42,140
I'm going to teach them a lesson.

634
00:31:42,980 --> 00:31:44,260
Now, you're locked up in here.

635
00:31:45,180 --> 00:31:46,660
I'm afraid you don't have a chance

636
00:31:48,980 --> 00:31:50,260
to take revenge on them.

637
00:31:51,220 --> 00:31:51,820
No.

638
00:31:52,540 --> 00:31:53,340
At that time,

639
00:31:53,500 --> 00:31:54,860
they indeed ran away.

640
00:31:55,460 --> 00:31:57,180
But they did that because of urgency.

641
00:32:00,100 --> 00:32:01,380
Why are you so sure?

642
00:32:04,020 --> 00:32:04,620
Why?

643
00:32:07,500 --> 00:32:09,500
I have a feeling. Well, it's hard to describe it.

644
00:32:11,300 --> 00:32:12,380
Feeling?

645
00:32:13,660 --> 00:32:14,500
Do you know

646
00:32:15,020 --> 00:32:16,340
what kind of person Wuxin is?

647
00:32:17,460 --> 00:32:18,020
Wuxin?

648
00:32:18,700 --> 00:32:19,700
Isn't he Abbot Wangyou's

649
00:32:19,740 --> 00:32:20,380
disciple?

650
00:32:22,660 --> 00:32:23,820
Even if he doesn't come,

651
00:32:24,180 --> 00:32:25,660
Xiao Se will come to save me.

652
00:32:26,860 --> 00:32:28,140
After all, I still owe Xiao Se

653
00:32:28,140 --> 00:32:29,340
500 silver taels.

654
00:32:30,460 --> 00:32:32,180
We shall wait and see, then.

655
00:32:36,100 --> 00:32:38,020
Enough about me. What about you?

656
00:32:38,660 --> 00:32:39,780
Don't you have friends who can rescue you?

657
00:32:41,140 --> 00:32:42,340
I've never had friends.

658
00:32:43,340 --> 00:32:44,300
I don't need any either.

659
00:32:46,620 --> 00:32:47,260
Then why

660
00:32:47,260 --> 00:32:48,100
did you come here alone?

661
00:32:49,780 --> 00:32:50,580
Me?

662
00:32:53,380 --> 00:32:56,020
I came here

663
00:32:58,020 --> 00:32:59,620
because I want to be the emperor!

664
00:33:05,540 --> 00:33:06,940
You want to be the emperor?

665
00:33:07,820 --> 00:33:09,300
Are you drunk?

666
00:33:09,860 --> 00:33:11,300
If you become the emperor,

667
00:33:11,620 --> 00:33:12,820
then I'm the Sword Deity.

668
00:33:13,300 --> 00:33:15,260
All right. If I become the emperor,

669
00:33:15,660 --> 00:33:17,020
I shall grant you that title!

670
00:33:17,780 --> 00:33:19,900
It's not a title an emperor can grant.

671
00:33:21,460 --> 00:33:22,700
You're pretty funny.

672
00:33:23,940 --> 00:33:24,460
Don't worry.

673
00:33:25,300 --> 00:33:26,340
When my friends come and rescue me,

674
00:33:26,620 --> 00:33:27,900
we'll save you too.

675
00:33:29,780 --> 00:33:30,300
Stop making so much noise!

676
00:33:32,660 --> 00:33:33,140
Get out.

677
00:33:40,260 --> 00:33:40,780
Where are you

678
00:33:40,780 --> 00:33:41,460
taking him?

679
00:33:42,820 --> 00:33:44,300
Mister, don't be scared!

680
00:33:45,180 --> 00:33:45,660
My friends

681
00:33:46,180 --> 00:33:47,380
will definitely come and save us!

682
00:33:53,780 --> 00:33:55,220
Master, please spare me.

683
00:33:55,540 --> 00:33:56,140
Hero, please spare me.

684
00:33:57,140 --> 00:33:58,500
Enough begging. So tell me.

685
00:33:59,420 --> 00:34:00,820
Where did you lock

686
00:34:01,300 --> 00:34:02,340
the man you caught this morning?

687
00:34:03,540 --> 00:34:05,380
I really don't know.

688
00:34:09,020 --> 00:34:10,300
Wait, I know.

689
00:34:10,780 --> 00:34:11,660
I suddenly remember where he's being locked up.

690
00:34:12,220 --> 00:34:13,220
All the hostages we kidnapped for ransom

691
00:34:13,940 --> 00:34:15,700
are in the dungeon.

692
00:34:16,260 --> 00:34:17,380
How many experts are there

693
00:34:17,660 --> 00:34:18,540
among the Long Arch Wing Chaser

694
00:34:19,180 --> 00:34:20,140
and the Night Parade of 100 Ghosts?

695
00:34:20,940 --> 00:34:21,620
What phase are they at?

696
00:34:22,580 --> 00:34:24,340
The one with the best martial arts skills

697
00:34:24,460 --> 00:34:25,300
is our boss.

698
00:34:26,140 --> 00:34:27,260
But two days ago,

699
00:34:27,340 --> 00:34:28,060
someone came to our stronghold.

700
00:34:28,500 --> 00:34:29,820
He looks like an expert too.

701
00:34:30,340 --> 00:34:31,820
The boss is very respectful of him

702
00:34:32,220 --> 00:34:34,460
and addresses him as Mister.

703
00:34:36,860 --> 00:34:37,460
Mister?

704
00:34:37,980 --> 00:34:41,980
[Dungeon]

705
00:34:48,860 --> 00:34:49,540
He's truly

706
00:34:49,660 --> 00:34:50,980
an inexperienced lad.

707
00:34:52,060 --> 00:34:52,420
Mister,

708
00:34:53,260 --> 00:34:54,380
will that person come
and break him out of the dungeon?

709
00:34:55,220 --> 00:34:56,020
Break him out?

710
00:34:57,260 --> 00:34:58,620
He's occupied with his own trouble

711
00:34:58,620 --> 00:34:59,940
and he can't even save himself.

712
00:35:00,300 --> 00:35:01,300
How can he break him out?

713
00:35:02,300 --> 00:35:03,500
If he really did come,

714
00:35:04,620 --> 00:35:06,020
I'd like to see him.

715
00:35:07,460 --> 00:35:09,260
(After all, I haven't seen him for a long time.)

716
00:35:10,220 --> 00:35:11,980
(The Young Head of Tianwaitian,)

717
00:35:12,460 --> 00:35:13,740
(Ye Anshi.)

718
00:35:53,540 --> 00:35:53,980
Lei Wujie.

719
00:35:55,940 --> 00:35:56,540
Lei Wujie.

720
00:35:57,660 --> 00:35:59,020
Xiao Se, I'm here.

721
00:35:59,980 --> 00:36:00,460
Catch the keys.

722
00:36:08,340 --> 00:36:09,100
I knew you'd come

723
00:36:09,140 --> 00:36:09,780
and save me.

724
00:36:10,620 --> 00:36:11,260
Did you drink liquor?

725
00:36:12,380 --> 00:36:12,740
Yes.

726
00:36:13,860 --> 00:36:14,500
There was a man

727
00:36:14,540 --> 00:36:15,220
who was locked up next to my cell.

728
00:36:15,620 --> 00:36:16,500
He was the one who gave me the liquor.

729
00:36:17,580 --> 00:36:19,260
I even told him we'd save him.

730
00:36:19,500 --> 00:36:20,700
But he was taken away by the guards.

731
00:36:21,140 --> 00:36:22,500
You sure enjoy your time here.

732
00:36:23,180 --> 00:36:24,460
You even had liquor in the dungeon.

733
00:36:29,380 --> 00:36:29,820
(This)

734
00:36:30,820 --> 00:36:32,090
(is Qiulubai liquor from Diaolou Parlor)

735
00:36:32,140 --> 00:36:32,780
(in Tianqi City.)

736
00:36:33,500 --> 00:36:34,540
(Why would someone be drinking)

737
00:36:34,620 --> 00:36:35,700
(such an expensive liquor at a place like this?)

738
00:36:36,780 --> 00:36:37,500
But where did he get

739
00:36:38,740 --> 00:36:39,460
the liquor?

740
00:36:40,660 --> 00:36:41,140
Right.

741
00:36:41,900 --> 00:36:43,100
Why did he have liquor?

742
00:36:46,820 --> 00:36:47,500
(Could it be...)

743
00:36:50,420 --> 00:36:51,860
Well, enough about him.

744
00:36:52,740 --> 00:36:53,220
Next,

745
00:36:53,820 --> 00:36:54,500
we'll start

746
00:36:54,500 --> 00:36:55,420
our real operation.

747
00:36:56,420 --> 00:36:57,980
I knew with your abilities,

748
00:36:58,340 --> 00:36:59,700
this foolish boy

749
00:37:00,220 --> 00:37:00,820
wouldn't get caught

750
00:37:00,860 --> 00:37:01,740
if you helped him during the day.

751
00:37:02,780 --> 00:37:03,740
Yet, you let him get caught

752
00:37:04,060 --> 00:37:04,940
and rescue him at night.

753
00:37:05,420 --> 00:37:06,620
You must have other plans.

754
00:37:07,580 --> 00:37:09,020
Tell me what it is.

755
00:37:15,900 --> 00:37:16,780
The play was supposed

756
00:37:16,820 --> 00:37:17,620
to have ended.

757
00:37:18,580 --> 00:37:19,500
What do you mean, mister?

758
00:37:20,620 --> 00:37:22,020
Tianwaitian wants to welcome

759
00:37:22,060 --> 00:37:23,220
their young head back.

760
00:37:23,820 --> 00:37:24,780
But some sects in the Central Plains

761
00:37:24,900 --> 00:37:26,220
don't want to let him leave.

762
00:37:26,820 --> 00:37:27,820
Some of them

763
00:37:27,900 --> 00:37:29,740
are after the Secret Rakshasa Arts.

764
00:37:30,100 --> 00:37:31,580
That's why there are so many people

765
00:37:31,660 --> 00:37:32,820
fighting over the Golden Coffin.

766
00:37:33,540 --> 00:37:34,820
But who would have thought

767
00:37:35,220 --> 00:37:37,020
the weiqi piece that people are after

768
00:37:37,380 --> 00:37:38,700
would leave the checkerboard?

769
00:37:40,460 --> 00:37:42,140
A weiqi piece without discipline

770
00:37:43,340 --> 00:37:45,900
will become a variable no matter where he goes.

771
00:37:46,940 --> 00:37:48,980
If he returns to Tianwaitian,

772
00:37:49,660 --> 00:37:50,660
we'll come into contact with him often

773
00:37:50,780 --> 00:37:51,740
in the future.

774
00:37:52,940 --> 00:37:54,460
So it's better to know more

775
00:37:54,540 --> 00:37:55,260
about him.

776
00:37:55,860 --> 00:37:56,540
You're right, mister.

777
00:37:58,220 --> 00:38:00,300
But it won't be easy

778
00:38:00,740 --> 00:38:01,780
for him to leave the checkerboard.

779
00:38:03,020 --> 00:38:04,980
No matter how skilled his qinggong is,

780
00:38:05,700 --> 00:38:08,100
can he stop the major power from watching him...

781
00:38:10,660 --> 00:38:11,100
Wait.

782
00:38:12,140 --> 00:38:12,780
I was wrong.

783
00:38:14,060 --> 00:38:15,180
He'll surely break that kid out of the dungeon!

784
00:38:16,940 --> 00:38:17,660
What's going on?

785
00:38:17,820 --> 00:38:18,820
(I'm Wuxin of Hanshui Temple.)

786
00:38:19,420 --> 00:38:20,020
(I especially come to visit)

787
00:38:20,060 --> 00:38:22,300
(the Long Arch Wing Chaser
and the Night Parade of 100 Ghosts.)

788
00:38:23,300 --> 00:38:23,740
Someone!

789
00:38:24,020 --> 00:38:25,780
Hurry!

790
00:38:26,180 --> 00:38:26,780
Fetch the water now!

791
00:38:27,220 --> 00:38:27,820
Coming!

792
00:38:27,940 --> 00:38:28,420
Move it!

793
00:38:28,660 --> 00:38:29,020
Hurry!

794
00:38:29,620 --> 00:38:30,020
Over here!

795
00:38:30,460 --> 00:38:30,740
This way!

796
00:38:33,180 --> 00:38:33,660
Hurry!

797
00:38:34,940 --> 00:38:35,300
Someone!

798
00:38:35,900 --> 00:38:36,300
Put out the fire!

799
00:38:36,540 --> 00:38:37,100
Call for help!

800
00:38:37,460 --> 00:38:37,860
Hurry!

801
00:38:38,140 --> 00:38:38,820
Fetch the water now!

802
00:38:39,060 --> 00:38:39,980
Stop them!

803
00:38:40,220 --> 00:38:41,140
After them now!

804
00:38:47,060 --> 00:38:47,700
Put out the fire!

805
00:38:47,900 --> 00:38:48,420
Don't let them escape!

806
00:38:50,460 --> 00:38:51,220
Stop them!

807
00:39:01,180 --> 00:39:02,140
(It must be a coincidence.)

808
00:39:03,100 --> 00:39:04,420
(Why would he come to a place like this?)

809
00:39:06,860 --> 00:39:07,780
(Perhaps I'm overthinking.)

810
00:39:29,700 --> 00:39:30,460
That's odd.

811
00:39:31,620 --> 00:39:32,540
Yushi may not be big.

812
00:39:33,260 --> 00:39:34,740
But it also trades with Beili.

813
00:39:35,700 --> 00:39:37,220
There may not be an endless stream
of traveling traders.

814
00:39:37,580 --> 00:39:38,980
But it shouldn't be this quiet.

815
00:39:39,500 --> 00:39:41,300
That's right. We've walked

816
00:39:41,500 --> 00:39:42,180
almost half a day now.

817
00:39:42,420 --> 00:39:43,460
But we didn't see a single person here.

818
00:39:44,020 --> 00:39:45,260
What's going on?

819
00:39:45,820 --> 00:39:46,900
Don't tell me

820
00:39:47,300 --> 00:39:48,220
something happened to Yushi.

821
00:39:49,620 --> 00:39:51,140
But I didn't hear anything about that.

822
00:39:52,340 --> 00:39:53,580
Is it possible
that they've changed the official route?

823
00:39:56,140 --> 00:39:57,100
Airhead.

824
00:39:57,700 --> 00:39:58,860
Do you think an official route

825
00:39:59,180 --> 00:40:00,100
is easy to change as you please?

826
00:40:01,180 --> 00:40:02,540
You pronounced it wrongly again.

827
00:40:04,340 --> 00:40:06,220
Enough. Let's stop walking.

828
00:40:06,860 --> 00:40:08,260
We're obviously lost.

829
00:40:09,740 --> 00:40:10,300
Wuxin,

830
00:40:11,140 --> 00:40:12,420
don't tell me you're bad at direction too.

831
00:40:13,660 --> 00:40:14,860
I've seen the map.

832
00:40:15,580 --> 00:40:16,370
There's only

833
00:40:16,700 --> 00:40:18,220
one official route to Yushi.

834
00:40:18,820 --> 00:40:19,500
How can we get lost

835
00:40:19,780 --> 00:40:20,740
when we follow the route?

836
00:40:22,540 --> 00:40:23,700
This isn't the official route.

837
00:40:24,340 --> 00:40:25,260
This path is obviously made

838
00:40:25,260 --> 00:40:26,140
by people who traveled on foot.

839
00:40:26,940 --> 00:40:28,180
Why would the map mark this route?

840
00:40:29,300 --> 00:40:30,420
You brought us here.

841
00:40:33,140 --> 00:40:33,820
It's hard

842
00:40:33,900 --> 00:40:35,500
for those who don't join cultivation in Nirvana

843
00:40:36,060 --> 00:40:37,500
to learn from each other.

844
00:40:38,260 --> 00:40:39,700
Stop showing off your literary skills.

845
00:40:40,460 --> 00:40:41,980
Ordinary people lose their way,

846
00:40:42,300 --> 00:40:44,900
and acting recklessly is an obsession.

847
00:40:55,180 --> 00:40:56,300
There's an inn ahead!

848
00:40:56,860 --> 00:40:57,900
